      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这是 Qwen2.5-VL 7B FP8 编码器，用于同时理解编辑指令和多张参考图。type 保持 qwen_image，device 通常保持 default。\n\n文件：qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/HunyuanVideo_1.5_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors?download=true\n存放：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\text_encoders\n\n仓库名称虽包含 HunyuanVideo，但这是官方 ComfyUI 工作流使用的同名编码器文件。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 117,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1360.4644775390625,
        190.4507293701172
      ],
      "size": [
        270,
        170
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 7,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "ModelSamplingAuraFlow 为模型设置正确的采样时间表。当前 shift=3 是本工作流的匹配值，通常无需修改。\n\n它应位于 LoRA 加载之后、CFGNorm 之前；断开或绕过会改变去噪轨迹和编辑效果。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 122,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1658.8619384765625,
        190.2154998779297
      ],
      "size": [
        319.23382568359375,
        330
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 8,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这是最终执行像素修复的采样节点，参数已与 8-step Lightning LoRA 对齐。\n\n• seed：randomize 每次结果不同；固定种子便于对比提示词。\n• steps：保持 8，与当前 LoRA 配套。\n• cfg：保持 1。\n• sampler：euler。\n• scheduler：simple。\n• denoise：当前 1 会完整执行编辑；像素修复若变化过大，可先通过提示词加强“保持不变”，再谨慎小幅降低 denoise。\n\n一次只调整一个参数，并先用单张图测试。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 118,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1363.965576171875,
        409.408447265625
      ],
      "size": [
        270,
        190
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 9,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "CFGNorm 用于稳定条件引导，抑制过曝、偏色和细节爆炸。当前 strength=1、pre_cfg=false 可作为稳定起点。\n\n像素修复出现过度重绘时，可小幅降低 strength 后对比；一次只改一个参数，并固定 seed。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 120,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1671.5223388671875,
        578.131103515625
      ],
      "size": [
        270,
        205
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 10,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "ReferenceLatent 把图像编辑条件与图1的潜空间关联起来，让模型在原图结构上执行修复，而不是从零生成。\n\nconditioning 来自多图编辑编码，latent 来自图1的 VAEEncode。两条线都必须保留，否则身份、构图和像素位置更容易漂移。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 119,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1366.754150390625,
        646.6325073242188
      ],
      "size": [
        270,
        175
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 11,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这个节点把编辑条件清零后送到 KSampler 的 negative 输入，配合 CFG=1 使用。\n\n保持现有连线即可，不需要额外填写负面提示词。像素修复中的禁止项应直接写进正向编辑指令。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 111,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        2539.136474609375,
        191.00791931152344
      ],
      "size": [
        313.97216796875,
        230
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 12,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这里预览并保存最终修复结果。filename_prefix 可设置文件名前缀，也可写成“项目名/前缀”建立子文件夹。\n\n默认目录：D:\\ComfyUI\\output\n\n该节点不需要下载模型。正式批量处理前先用一张图片检查修复强度、细节一致性和输出文件名。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 115,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        2082.102783203125,
        -33.09373092651367
      ],
      "size": [
        317.1868591308594,
        217.47418212890625
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 13,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "VAE 同时参与参考图编码和结果解码，必须使用 Qwen-Image 专用文件。若选错 VAE，常见表现是通道报错、花屏、偏色或无法解码。\n\n文件：qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors?download=true\n存放：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\vae\n\n下载后刷新模型列表并选择同名文件。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 113,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -746.7987060546875,
        438.3532409667969
      ],
      "size": [
        473.89166259765625,
        172.4944610595703
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 14,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这个 LoRA 把 Qwen-Image-Edit-2511 加速到 8 步，必须与下游 KSampler 的 steps=8 配套。strength_model 建议保持 1；降低会减弱加速效果，随意更换旧版 Qwen-Image LoRA 可能造成编辑失败或画质异常。\n\n文件：Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-bf16.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-bf16.safetensors?download=true\n存放：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\loras"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 107,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -191.20884704589844,
        37.8177604675293
      ],
      "size": [
        429.27471923828125,
        225.20285034179688
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 15,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "这里填写图像编辑指令，并自动传给正向编码节点。默认提示词适合像素修复。\n\n描述时先说“修复什么”，再明确“哪些内容必须保持不变”。局部修复要指出位置、颜色、材质和边缘关系；避免只写“变清晰”，否则模型容易重绘整张图。\n\n需要改变内容时，请删除默认提示中对应的“保持不变”限制。"
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -1364.468994140625,
        -339.090576171875
      ],
      "size": [
        540,
        720
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 16,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "我是卡卡，这是一个 Qwen-Image-Edit-2511 多图像素修复工作流。图1是要修复的主图，图2、图3用于补充参考；没有参考图时也可重复使用主图。欢迎加我好友一起交流学习，微信：kkcomfy\n\n【使用前准备】\n建议先更新 ComfyUI。下载模型后放入对应目录，再刷新模型列表或重启。\n\n1. 扩散模型\n文件：qwen_image_edit_2511_bf16.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image-Edit_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/qwen_image_edit_2511_bf16.safetensors?download=true\n目录：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\diffusion_models\n\n2. 8 步 Lightning LoRA\n文件：Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-bf16.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511-Lightning-8steps-V1.0-bf16.safetensors?download=true\n目录：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\loras\n\n3. 文本/视觉编码器\n文件：qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/HunyuanVideo_1.5_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors?download=true\n目录：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\text_encoders\n\n4. VAE\n文件：qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors?download=true\n目录：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\vae\n\n官方模型介绍：https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen-Image-Edit-2511"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
